  DISEASES & MEDICINE
============================================================

Disease:     Polio
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Poliovirus
Transmission:Fecal-oral
Symptoms:    Paralysis in severe cases
Treatment:   No cure; supportive care
Deaths/yr:   0M
Vaccine:     Yes (near-eradicated)
Discovered:  1840

Disease:     Hepatitis B
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    HBV
Transmission:Blood, sexual contact
Symptoms:    Often asymptomatic; jaundice
Treatment:   Antivirals (tenofovir)
Deaths/yr:   0.82M
Vaccine:     Yes (highly effective)
Discovered:  1965

Disease:     Diabetes Type 2
Type:        Metabolic
Pathogen:    Non-communicable
Transmission:Lifestyle
Symptoms:    Thirst, frequent urination, fatigue
Treatment:   Metformin, lifestyle, insulin
Deaths/yr:   1.5M
Vaccine:     No
Discovered:  1922

